snippet.title: Canon in D - River Flows in You (Orchestral Arrangement / Mashup)
snippet.description:
Happy Valentine's Day everyone!~ ♥ 

I finished this arrangement the middle of last year but just never uploaded it. This was actually a birthday gift to another friend but I came across it again and liked how it turned out, so what better day to upload it than today? ;D 
These two songs were the pieces that my friend played for me on piano, which was why I decided to use them. Then as I was arranging the two, I thought: let's combine the two pieces somehow! And so I figured out a way to mix the two lovely songs toward the end~ 

I've also received a ton of requests for the score of this arrangement which I've now included down below!
Enjoy!~ 

~Roze

Songs: 
Canon in D - Johann Pachelbel
River Flows in You - Yiruma
Arranged and Mixed by: Roze

MP3: http://www.mediafire.com/download/eh6wo7iirva0kv1/Canon+in+D+-+River+Flows+in+You.mp3
Picture Link: http://anime-pictures.net/pictures/view_post/89361?lang=en

**Full Score: http://www.mediafire.com/file/q00sxl3hhsvfafh/Canon+in+D+-+River+Flows+in+You.pdf
